{
  "stem": "17301.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, there was one little girl who was all by herself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took her with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we helped her as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the food was a lot better than it was in the A lager.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, I guess, we needed a little more energy to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they-- they treated us a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- I forgot to tell you that each day after work, they took us to the shower.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they were afraid of any-- because we got in touch with so many-- we handled so many different clothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were a lot of germs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they took us for us to take a shower every single day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that was a big plus for us, as-- as far as we were concerned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Kanada was where people would come in from other-- other lagers, and-- and take the clothing that we bundled up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made it into a bundle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would take it out, and supposedly they-- they took all that-- all those-- that clothing into Germany to use it for whatever they were going to use it for.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's what we did for a while, yes, for a long time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to make bundles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one-- one day I was assigned to go to a-- like a heap of eyeglasses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean it was-- the eyeglasses were like in a mound, I mean, huge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was separate eyeglasses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were shoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That there were-- there was hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was-- I started-- they asked me to select certain eyeglasses, which I started to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I guess I didn't do a very good job of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
